QtGui.QDesktopServices.storageLocation(QtGui.QDesktopServices.DataLocation)
{code}

Note, that Qt4 -> Qt5 [guide|https://wiki.qt.io/Transition_from_Qt_4.x_to_Qt5#QDesktopServices::storageLocation_deprecated] suggests to use:
{code}
QStandardPaths::standardLocations(QStandardPaths::DataLocation)
{code}
but QStandardPaths not available in PySide2

