Qmake lacks the possibility to enable scopes based on qt version being newer or older than a specific qt version (ex 5.7.1).
Currently, one needs to test (major > 5) || ((major == 5) && ((minor > 7) || ((minor == 7) && (patch > 0)))), which is hard to read, and I'm not even sure it can be written in qmake language.

